'''罗杰·希尔斯曼'''（{{lang-en|'''Roger Hilsman Jr.'''}}，{{bd|1919年|11月23日|2014年|2月23日|catIdx=R}}），[[美国|美国]]政治人物、作家。曾担任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]的顾问、[[远东事务助理国务卿|远东事务助理国务卿]]，是[[越南战争|越南战争]]中政策制定的关键人物。<ref>[https://nsarchive2.gwu.edu/coldwar/interviews/episode-11/hilsman1.html ROGER HILSMAN - The National Security Archive]</ref><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/11/us/politics/roger-hilsman-adviser-to-kennedy-on-vietnam-dies-at-94.html Roger Hilsman, Adviser to Kennedy on Vietnam, Dies at 94]</ref><ref>[https://www.mtholyoke.edu/acad/intrel/pentagon2/doc115.htm Roger Hilsman, Department of State, Bureau of Intelligence and Research, Research Memorandum, RFE-27, June 18, 1962, "Progress Report on South Vietnam"]</ref>

